            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Once every hour as a full action, a morrigna can spin an invisible, magical spider out of their web shroud. This spider functions as the sensor of an <i>arcane eye</i> spell, although the morrigna does not need to concentrate to use the arachnid spy.",
